### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5230/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Basic Search - Find posts by keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=test
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Search with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=string&page=1&pageSize=2
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Case-Insensitive Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=HELLO
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Search by Category
# First get category ID from /api/categories
# Replace CATEGORY_ID_HERE with actual category ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=post&categoryId=CATEGORY_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Search Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/categories?q=tech
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Admin Advanced Search - Include Unpublished Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/admin?q=test&includeUnpublished=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Validation Error - Query Too Short
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=ab
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Validation Error - Empty Query
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. No Results Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=nonexistentquery123
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Multiple Page Navigation
# Page 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=string&page=1&pageSize=2
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=string&page=2&pageSize=2
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Search in Content (not just title)
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=comments
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. Get All Categories for Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

### Notes:
# - Minimum query length: 3 characters
# - Default page size: 20
# - Content is truncated to 200 characters in preview
# - Public search only shows published posts
# - Admin search can include unpublished posts with includeUnpublished=true
# - Search is case-insensitive
# - Searches in both Title and Content fields
